SELECT CHAR(VALUE('$$DD01 UPDATE EDIT=(1,0,C''&PARTI'',C'''     ||              
RTRIM(CHAR(PFRASFUN.FRDJFILST(DATE('&DATE')))) || ''')' ||                      
          REPEAT(' ',36)                                                        
          ,' ') )                                                               
FROM SYSIBM.SYSDUMMY1 ;                                                         
